 is  1.25 Crores (Rupees One \nCrore Twenty Five Lakhs Only). The said remuneration \nexcludes applicable taxes and out of pocket expenses.", "metadata": {"source": "/content/drive/MyDrive/pidilite/Annual-Report-2022-2023.pdf", "page": 273}, "type": "Document"}}